<h3>Intro&nbsp;</h3>
<p>def : as per LCI (267) , incitement to hatred primarily against a group of persons on basis of race, ethnicity, sexual orientation, religion etc</p>
<p>FR has RR.</p>
<p>Reasons - include online hate speech</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Way forward</h3>
<ol>
<li>TK vishwanathan committee
<ol>
<li>Cybercrime Coordinator = strictly regulate cyber space for hatred and incitement to violence</li>
<li>make strict laws = Add "prevent spreading hatred" to<span style="color:#e67e22"><em><strong>153C </strong></em></span>of IPC&nbsp;</li></ol></li>
<li>SC (2020) : Stopping hate crime on TV is essential.&nbsp;
<ol>
<li><strong>Preventing it (reporting hateful content) is similar to putting physical barricading.</strong> Preventing instigation is like giving lathi to policemen.</li>
<li>Reporting truth is not a problem. <em>TONE of reporting to AGITATE is.</em></li></ol></li>
<li><strong><em>News Broascasting standards authority - </em></strong>self regulatory body</li></ol>